title: Paquito D'Rivera, Love of Music, Grammy Award Winner
fulltitle: Paquito D'Rivera, Love of Music, Grammy Award Winner

description:
Paquito D'Rivera, Musician/Composer/Author/Bandleader talks about his love of music and how he won 11 Grammy Awards, but says he never worked just for the awards. 

1/23/14 #1529
